pageTitle: No menu plan, just the 3-day walk training schedule… | Angela's Kitchen
textBeforeTable: Countdown: 5 Weeks Your Training Schedule for This Week: What I do know is that Elette Gamble who works at Lakewinds (the store where I hold my gluten and dairy free classes) is also planning on doing the 3-Day walk.  If I am not able to walk, maybe I can encourage some of you to donate to Elette’s fundraising.  She is celebrating her 5 years of Survival from breast cancer.  Please support her journey.  Thanks! Well, I think I need to embrace the fact that I may not be doing the 3-day walk…  4 people donating does not a walk make.  Sigh…  I am feeling a bit down about it.  However, maybe my efforts toward a garage sale will help.  We will see. | Leave a comment July 20, 2009 Posted on No menu plan, just the 3-day walk training schedule… Mayo Clinic study finds celiac disease 4 times more common than in 1950s → ← Gluten Freezer Friday – Chicken and Rosemary Roasted Veggies
